Feature: Login to zen portal
  As a registered user
  I want to log in and log out of the zen portal application
  So that I can see and secure my course progress

  Background:
    Given the user is on the zen portal login page

 @smoke @login
  Scenario Outline: Successful login and logout
    When the user logs in with username "<username>" and password "<password>"
    Then the user should be redirected to the dashboard page
    When the user clicks on the logout button
    Then the user should be redirected back to the login page

    Examples: Valid user
      | username            | password    |
      | sap180996@gmail.com | Padmini@123 |

  @regression @login @negative
  Scenario Outline: Login attempts with different user types
    When the user logs in with username "<username>" and password "<password>"
    Then the login result should be "<expected_result>"

    Examples: Invalid user types
      | username            | password | expected_result |
      | sap180996@gmail.com | Padmini  | Invalid         |

